```

Add these dependency injections AFTER the existing `@Resource private PermissionChecker permissionChecker;` field (check if they already exist):
```java
    @Resource
    private INodeShareService nodeShareService;

    @Resource
    private ISpaceNodeService spaceNodeService;
```

Add this new endpoint method. Place it AFTER the `listManagedSpaceForMigration` method (around line 118) and BEFORE the `copyFile` method (around line 121):

```java
    @PostResource(path = "/nodeFolderPath", requiredPermission = false)
    @Operation(summary = "Get source node folder path for migration path matching")
    public ResponseData<List<FolderPathItem>> getNodeFolderPath(@RequestBody @Valid NodeFolderPathRo ro) {
        // 通过 shareId 鉴权
        NodeShareEntity nodeShareEntity = nodeShareService.getByShareId(ro.getShareId());
        if (nodeShareEntity == null || Boolean.FALSE.equals(nodeShareEntity.getIsEnabled())) {
            throw new BusinessException(NodeShareException.SHARE_FORBIDDEN);
        }
        SpaceNodeEntity spaceNodeEntity = spaceNodeService.getById(nodeShareEntity.getSpaceNodeId());
        if (spaceNodeEntity == null) {
            throw new BusinessException(NodeShareException.NODE_NOT_FOUND_OR_DELETED);
        }
        NodeShareProps props = NodeShareProps.fromBits(nodeShareEntity.getPropsBits());
        if (!props.getCanBeStored()) {
            throw new BusinessException(NodeShareException.NODE_SHARE_FORBID_STORE);
        }

        List<FolderPathItem> path = spaceNodeMigrationQueryManager.getNodeFolderPath(ro.getSpaceNodeId());
        return ResponseData.success(path);
    }
```

